599
00:58:09,860 --> 00:58:10,929
Hye Yum.

600
00:58:36,550 --> 00:58:39,150
Mata awak bermasalahkah?

601
00:58:39,420 --> 00:58:42,119
Dia tak nampak macam Wang Yu.

602
00:58:46,059 --> 00:58:47,460
Saya minta maaf.

603
